{
  "stem": "19211.1",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 287.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "That's when the war started, in 1941, with the Russians.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And within two to three weeks, they occupied us.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "The Germans occupied us.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "That's when the big trouble started, when they occupied us.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "It started getting very bad.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "First of all, they-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] hunger.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They were taking all the food from the farmers.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The farmers didn't have much food.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And there were, were rations.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They gave us rations.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And of course, the Jews suffered the most.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "They gave us very little food to eat.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And there was-- that's what we felt first was hunger.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And then progressively, they did other things.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "They took the-- all the intelligentsia and all the people that were educated, took them away.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And they killed them all, which we found out later.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, they had to register.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "There was a Judenrat, which was a Jewish organization.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And they had to register there.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And they didn't know where they were going.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they took them.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we found out later that they killed them all.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "It might-- maybe it was 400 or 500 people-- doctors, lawyers, other professionals, businessmen.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And then what was left was uneducated, which is, basically speaking, just plain-- they, they could control them better.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And I-- that's-- all these things I found out later.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And that's what happened.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "That was bad.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And I think they were also sending Einsatzgruppen.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "They called it Einsatzgruppen, which is the SS.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And they were just taking Jews out into the woods and killing them there.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Randomly, they were catching them on the streets.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And it was very difficult.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We had to wear our armbands with the Jewish star.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And, and we were afraid to go out.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "It was-- it was pretty, pretty lousy.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In 1940-- I was born in '28.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
